-- AB InBev declines to comment on reports of Modelo interest
-- 
-- Mon Jun 25, 2012 7:06am EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2012/06/25/us-modelo-abinbev-abinbev-idUSBRE85O06X20120625

 

 BRUSSELS  (Reuters) - Anheuser-Busch InBev ( ABI.BR ) declined to comment on Monday on reports it was close to buying the 50 percent of Corona beer maker Grupo Modelo ( GMODELOC.MX ) it does not already own. 
 A person familiar with the matter earlier told Reuters that a potential deal could top $10 billion. (Reporting By Philip Blenkinsop)